@startuml
title Ott Based System Mini Reel State Machine

state "Initial" as Initial
state "Account Created" as AccountCreated
state "Watching Videos" as WatchingVideos
state "Uploading Videos" as UploadingVideos
state "Saving to Likes" as SavingToLikes
state "Viewing Saved Videos" as ViewingSavedVideos
state "Discussion" as Discussion

[*] --> Initial : Start

Initial --> AccountCreated : Create Account

AccountCreated --> WatchingVideos : Watch Videos
WatchingVideos --> UploadingVideos : Upload Video
UploadingVideos --> WatchingVideos : Back to Watching
WatchingVideos --> SavingToLikes : Save to Likes
SavingToLikes --> ViewingSavedVideos : View Saved
ViewingSavedVideos --> WatchingVideos : Continue Watching
ViewingSavedVideos --> Discussion : Enter Discussion

Discussion --> AccountCreated : Finish Discussion

AccountCreated --> ViewingSavedVideos : View Saved Videos
ViewingSavedVideos --> AccountCreated : Back to Account

@enduml
